Class NotificationCollection<E>

  • java.lang.Object

    public abstract class NotificationCollection<E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Collection<E>
    Base class with methods to ignore creating copy for event. It is not implementation ofCollection NOTE - As of now, no event generated on stream based operation.
